item.title: Hummingbird notebook
item.dc:creator: lylephuong
item.description: 120 sheets notebook with hard cover made of recycled cardboard. 16x22cm
item.content:encoded: The Mountain fox notebook is the best option to write down your most ingenious ideas. At work, at home or when traveling, its endearing design and manufacturing quality will make you feel like writing! 90 gsm paper / double spiral binding.

item.title: Mug Today is a good day
item.dc:creator: lylephuong
item.description: Add an optimistic touch to your morning coffee and start the day in a good mood! 8,2cm diameter / 9,5cm height / 0.43kg. Dishwasher-proof.

item.title: Mug The adventure begins
item.dc:creator: lylephuong
item.content:encoded: The adventure begins with a cup of coffee. Set out to conquer the day! 8,2cm diameter / 9,5cm height / 0.43kg. Dishwasher-proof.

item.title: Hummingbird printed sweater
item.dc:creator: lylephuong
item.description: Regular fit, round neckline, long sleeves. 100% cotton, brushed inner side for extra comfort.
item.content:encoded: Studio Design’ PolyFaune collection features classic products with colorful patterns, inspired by the traditional japanese origamis. To wear with a chino or jeans. The sublimation textile printing process provides an exceptional color rendering and a color, guaranteed overtime.

item.title: Hummingbird printed t-shirt
item.dc:creator: lylephuong
item.description: Regular fit, round neckline, short sleeves. Made of extra long staple pima cotton.
item.content:encoded: Symbol of lightness and delicacy, the hummingbird evokes curiosity and joy. Studio Design’ PolyFaune collection features classic products with colorful patterns, inspired by the traditional japanese origamis. To wear with a chino or jeans. The sublimation textile printing process provides an exceptional color rendering and a color, guaranteed overtime.
